This is a sample blog post demonstrating how MDX content works with the portfolio. You can use **bold**, *italic*, and `inline code` in your posts.

## Code Blocks

Here's a code example:

```tsx
function Greeting({ name }: { name: string }) {
  return <h1>Hello, {name}!</h1>;
}
```

